<div id="review_1803362615" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1803362615" />
    <a title="Carolyn" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5562745-carolyn"><img alt="Carolyn" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1431486418p2/5562745.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1803362615?book_show_action=true">Nov 05, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Carolyn" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Carolyn" href="/user/show/5562745-carolyn">Carolyn</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1803362615" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10277202611715026814">Face-to-face with the desire to touch. <br/><br/>The book is a gesture I hold between my fingers ... a moan for the sake of a gesture (or is it a death croak, <i>la pètite morte</i>?) <br/><br/>The book is a gesture I hold between my teeth. Gnawing at the wound, mouth-born paroxysms of pain. <br/><br/>I pry the shards from crevasses of molars. Regurgitated, spit-soaked, soured by the sanguine, the little shredded book falls from my mouth into the soil. <br/><br/>Later, a paperwhite blooms beneath the snow.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


